headline: AI’s Future, What To Do When You Get Fired?

headline: Accenture’s Frontier Alliance Role And AI Culture Shift Raise Valuation Question
summary: Accenture (NYSE:ACN) has been named an anchor partner in OpenAI’s new enterprise focused Frontier Alliance, aimed at accelerating AI adoption across corporate workflows.
